item.title: CVE-2021-38358|2024-09-16T20:31:34.842Z -- moolamojo -- moolamojo
item.description: The MoolaMojo WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting via the classes parameter found in the ~/views/button-generator.html.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 0.7.4.1.
